## Frontend (Vite) environment variables
## Copy to `.env.local` for local development.

# REST API base URL for axios. Recommended: keep relative and use Vite proxy.
VITE_API_URL=/api

# Backend origin (used to resolve media URLs like `/uploads/...` and also used by Vite proxy).
VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8080

# WebSocket (SockJS) endpoint. Recommended: keep relative and use Vite proxy.
VITE_WS_URL=/ws/chat

# Python AI Engine base URL (optional).
VITE_AI_ENGINE_URL=http://localhost:8000

